<dl id="n06157f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06157f">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06157f"> 157(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> new mercies every day</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[from the FOURTH PETITION]</font> He has promised to supply all our need; <mark>His mercies are new every morning</mark>; He knoweth that we have need of these things; He has promised, Every day will I bless thee. <small> Anonymous, <a name="ATCC" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#ATCC"><cite title="source">Analysis of the Church Catechism</cite></a> (1879) 46</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
